{"tid":1457060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「一句講晒」有冇打算長期佔領機場？","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:44:07.000Z","uid":58276,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b60c6d347b289cab02996ca63dd438f260575105","tid":1457060,"uid":58276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:11:52.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有，長期佔領，直到政府答應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無，用日日清日日佔既方法，雖然唔可以完全癱瘓機場，但都可以影響到運作，如果日日都停到離境航班，政府一樣會跪低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個人支持日日清日日佔既方法，要長期佔領既人數太多，太多人要返工，頂唔到落去<br />\n<br />\n不過當然個策略都係要set dead line &gt; 行動升級"},{"pid":"336956dc0699cc2aaaa9915ce1162b2af45855ef","tid":1457060,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"日日清日日佔，捱唔到好耐"},{"pid":"0fc85f64d9952bc908621b2ec486a1274a38ceda","tid":1457060,"uid":58276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"336956dc0699cc2aaaa9915ce1162b2af45855ef","tid":1457060,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"日日清日日佔，捱唔到好耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:25:40.000Z","msg":"我都覺得捱唔到好耐，<br />\n但長期佔領都一樣要同時間鬥<br />\n如果每日都有咁多人，可以長期佔當然係最好<br />\n但對唔住，好多人都真係要返工，<br />\n請假既日子有限，包括我<br />\n<br />\n所以比較過人力，安全同可行性<br />\n我始終覺得日日清嘅方法係可取啲"},{"pid":"ca384138b4678608a3ad705fad4e3f702826f0bc","tid":1457060,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:26:05.000Z","msg":"Sorry ching 借位 求推<br />\n<br />\n突發！ 816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2403c4a5d5b16502fc13d15d992b77ce8303229f","tid":1457060,"uid":58276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"cc56ba1d2e2568c4a8873726bd8d7d003ceaec90","tid":1457060,"uid":21544,"like":0,